---
import BaseLayout from "../layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout title="Roadmap — GinkgoQ" description="Explore the public roadmap and build log for GinkgoQ's AI systems and publishing work.">
  <section class="roadmap-hero container" aria-labelledby="roadmap-heading">
    <span class="eyebrow">What's next</span>
    <h1 id="roadmap-heading">Publishing roadmap and build log</h1>
    <p class="lead">Upcoming content, current focus areas, and what we're working on next.</p>
  </section>

  <section class="roadmap-body container">
    <div class="roadmap-grid">
      <article class="roadmap-card">
        <h2>Current priorities</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>In-depth guides on designing extraction pipelines for structured data.</li>
          <li>Building evaluation frameworks that matter for production systems.</li>
          <li>System architecture patterns for reliable, scalable AI deployment.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>

      <article class="roadmap-card">
        <h2>Coming soon</h2>
        <ul>
          <li>Case studies on moving from prototype to production AI systems.</li>
          <li>Technical analysis of reliability patterns and failure modes.</li>
          <li>Practical guides on dataset development and validation strategies.</li>
        </ul>
      </article>
    </div>

    <div class="roadmap-note">
      <h2>Stay updated</h2>
      <p>Subscribe via RSS to get new posts and updates delivered automatically. Check back here as we progress through our content roadmap and publish new guides, case studies, and technical analysis.</p>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>

<style>
  .roadmap-hero {
    padding: 90px 0 50px;
    border-bottom: 1px solid var(--color-line);
  }

  .roadmap-hero h1 {
    max-width: 760px;
    margin: 1.1rem 0 1.4rem;
    font-size: clamp(3rem, 5vw, 4.2rem);
    line-height: 1.02;
  }

  .roadmap-body {
    padding: 64px 0 96px;
    display: grid;
    gap: 2.25rem;
  }

  .roadmap-grid {
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(2, minmax(0, 1fr));
    gap: 1.75rem;
  }

  .roadmap-card {
    padding: 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
  }

  .roadmap-card h2 {
    margin: 0 0 1rem;
  }

  .roadmap-card ul {
    margin: 0;
    padding-left: 1.1rem;
    color: var(--color-muted);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .roadmap-note {
    padding: 1.9rem 2rem;
    border: 1px solid var(--color-line);
    border-radius: var(--radius-md);
    background: var(--color-surface-2);
  }

  .roadmap-note h2 {
    margin-top: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 980px) {
    .roadmap-grid {
      grid-template-columns: 1fr;
    }
  }
</style>
